{"tid":406231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【慎入】3人遭毒梟斬首紮成木乃伊，頭顱擺入帽棄屍街頭","createTime":"2017-09-19T13:03:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T17:44:48.000Z","uid":30040,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"47d9f26c643a3722bc63785a8c931e4c518936c3","tid":406231,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T13:03:19.000Z","msg":"墨西哥不少城市黑幫毒梟橫行，隨之而來的就是暴力及血腥罪行，哈拉帕（Xalapa）警方上周就發現3位遭毒梟私刑處決的死者，他們均被斬首，頭顱就放入傳統的帽內被棄屍街頭，死狀恐怖。<br />\n<br />\n由照片所見，三具遺體都紮滿黑色垃圾膠袋及膠紙變成「木乃伊」，他們都身首異處，頭顱被墨西哥帽蓋著。有些頭顱被放到屍體的胸口，有些就放在屍體旁邊。<br />\n<br />\n報道指3名死者在上周二失蹤，翌日就被發現棄屍街頭，警方相信是販毒集團份子所為。<br />\n<br />\n因黑幫毒梟之間的幫派鬥爭而引起的血案時有發生，除了槍殺，分屍案亦不時出現。度假勝地阿卡普爾科（Acapulco）的居民說，時常在街上或海灘見到屍體，令度假天堂變成「世上最危險城市之一」。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》/馬來西亞《中國報》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170919/large/1505789320_f776.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170919%2Flarge%2F1505789320_f776.jpg&h=41a76220&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170919/large/1505789322_e74b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170919%2Flarge%2F1505789322_e74b.jpg&h=50f87093&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170919/large/1505789323_0754.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170919%2Flarge%2F1505789323_0754.jpg&h=00b53672&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fcd3257ce3724d6f6ff98eb88f545d494a2bc178","tid":406231,"uid":28031,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T13:05:24.000Z","msg":"有格仔慎咩入呀<br />\n無碼呢？"},{"pid":"b0a63c811104d87817cb31aebb3e791aa7488da1","tid":406231,"uid":6548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T13:18:19.000Z","msg":"放無碼出黎啦 無碼有咩咁好睇"},{"pid":"e6d4ce